<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" class="h-full bg-gray-50">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <% if (siteSettings && (siteSettings.favicon_url || siteSettings.logo_url)) { %>
      <link rel="icon" href="<%= siteSettings.favicon_url || siteSettings.logo_url %>" />
    <% } %>
    <title>비밀번호 찾기 - <%= (siteSettings && siteSettings.company_name) ? siteSettings.company_name : '관리자' %></title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="h-full flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <% if (siteSettings && siteSettings.logo_url) { %>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="<%= siteSettings.logo_url %>" alt="" class="h-16 sm:h-20 w-auto object-contain" />
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            <%= (siteSettings && siteSettings.company_name) ? siteSettings.company_name : '관리자' %>
          </h1>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">비밀번호 찾기</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
          관리자 아이디와 <b>계정에 등록된 이메일</b>을 입력하면 그 메일로 임시 비밀번호를 보내 드립니다.
        </p>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="mb-4 p-3 rounded-lg bg-red-50 border border-red-200 text-red-700 text-sm">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle mr-2"></i><%= error %>
          </div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (notice) { %>
          <div class="mb-4 p-3 rounded-lg bg-green-50 border border-green-200 text-green-800 text-sm">
            <i class="bi bi-envelope-check mr-2"></i><%= notice %>
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="POST" action="/admin/login/forgot" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="username" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5">아이디</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required autofocus autocomplete="username"
                   class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5">등록된 이메일</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email"
                   class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500" />
          </div>
          <button type="submit"
                  class="w-full h-[42px] rounded-lg bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            임시 비밀번호 받기
          </button>
        </form>

        <div class="mt-6 pt-5 border-t border-gray-100 text-center">
          <a href="/admin/login" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">로그인 화면으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          이메일이 등록돼 있지 않거나 메일을 받을 수 없다면, 다른 최고관리자에게
          <b>운영자 관리</b> 화면에서 비밀번호 초기화를 요청하세요.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
